\change_deleted 0 1271547664
Furthermore, 
\change_inserted 0 1271566301
d573 3
a575 8
CVaR is a more reliable risk measure than VaR under non-normal and non-continuou
s probability distributions because it is a “coherent risk measure” and
 is “sub-additive and convex” (
\change_deleted 0 1271547681
p.
 3, 
\change_unchanged
Krohmal, Palmquist, and Uryasev, 2002).
