 the sum of the CVaR of the weight
\change_inserted 0 1271566417
ed
\change_deleted 0 1271566415
s of the
\change_unchanged
 individual asset classes; furthermore, it can be extended from continuous
 probability distributions to discrete scenarios, allowing for optimization
 using simulations or discrete distributions and eliminating anomalous results
 such as multiple local minima.
